there is no political solution he said and a palestinian 
state in the occupied territories would be another terrorist 
state between libya and syria which would try to take over all of 
israel 
as long as the arab nation doesnt relinquish its plan to 
destroy the land of israel there will unfortunately be no peaceful 
solution begin declared 
the son was born in israel and unlike his father rarely 
invokes the nazi holocaust as a rationale for his political views 
he also is more softspoken 
he has a doctorate in geology from colorado state university and 
