ovando gunned down while on the way home from a political strategy 
session 
xavier has fallen because he was fighting for mexico to have a 
true and authentic democracy cardenas said he died because he 
dreamed of a better an independent and a free mexico 
that moment was like a snapshot capturing the campaign and the 
candidate 
