ultimate product of a system his father the late president lazaro 
cardenas helped create 
cardenas flourished in the pri he was its governor in michoacan 
and also a senator the break started last year when cardenas 
seemed to sense the growing force of a cold wind of disfavor that 
was about to blast the pri 
calling his movement the democratic current he told the party 
to hold a presidential primary the traditionalists in the party 
refused and cardenas defected forming a leftofcenter coalition 
the national democratic front 
when he decided to run for president he campaigned virtually 
without a critical forum television tv in mexico is 
governmentcontrolled or progovernment 
but as he traveled the nation he gathered larger and larger 
crowds winning the support of peasants students the struggling 
middle class intellectuals and oil workers 
about a month before the election he did what was considered 
impossible he unified the left the candidate of the mexican 
socialist party the largest organized leftist force dropped out 
and endorsed cardenas 
no one knows if that political unity will survive once the 
campaign passions cool but cardenas now appears to command a 
popular force the governing party cannot ignore 
