commodities trading company disagreed with the governments 
predictions on corn 
in all probability the corn crop will be lower and the 
carryover surplus predicted by the government to be 4 billion 
bushels will be lower the corn figures i think were going to 
view with some skepticism frazier said 
were not supposed to do that with government reports but i 
dont think we can help it he added 
