occurred as two policemen were taking a 25yearold prisoner from 
the courthouse to his cell 
he said about 30 palestinians tried to free the prisoner and 
four other officers rushed to the scene to drive back the crowd 
one policeman suffered a broken hand and the others had minor 
injuries he said 
four of the attackers were finally subdued and arrested 
lapidot said the others managed to escape 
