percent of the nations hispanics through 450 stations and cable 
channels 
and since 1985 reliance capitals telemundo network has spent 
more than 300 million to build a network in 16 markets reaching 
about 60 percent of the nations 18 millionplus hispanics 
when youre david and the other guy is goliath you try new 
things said telemundo chief henry silverman 
in early 1987 both networks beefed up us news programs but 
